snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin The Drum Master Official Release
snippet.description:
Taiko no Tatsujin The Drum Master is officially out on Xbox Series and Windows PC! With over 70 songs to choose from, you'll never stop drumming with Don and Ka. What's more, you can now play with your friends in local multiplayer mode and online ranked matches too!

#TaikonoTatsujin #BandaiNamco
